            <li><strong>SMS-kod kelmadi.</strong> Mobil aloqani tekshiring, qayta urining yoki bank operatoriga qo'ng'iroq qiling.</li>
            <li><strong>Click/Payme sahifasi ochilmadi.</strong> Brauzer keshini tozalang yoki Telegram ichidagi web view o'rniga tashqi brauzerda oching.</li>
